rows.label: qst102209_msg0003
rows.name:
There was nothing I could do... I hid
Corden in here so he wouldn't fall,
but his wounds were too deep...

rows.label: qst102209_msg0004
rows.name:
They're all dead...
It's all my fault again...

rows.label: qst102209_msg0006
rows.name:
Let's give the casualties a proper
burial, then head back to the village.

rows.label: qst102209_msg0007
rows.name:
You head back, too. I'd like to
talk to you at Mercenary HQ.
